# One regex per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
# Example: ignore links that 403 from CI but resolve fine in a browser.
# https://www\.example\.com/.*

# /stats is a GitHub Pages "clean URL" (it serves stats.html). The local static
# server used by this link check can't do clean URLs, so /stats 404s locally —
# but it resolves on the deployed site (mojito.wells.ee/stats). Scope the ignore
# to the local server so the real URL is still validated if referenced absolutely.
localhost:[0-9]+/stats$
